<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1242] The admin System handler returns bad JVM info</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1242</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;FileUtils.byteCountToDisplaySize has a funny way of converting. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;runtime.maxMemory() : 2092236800 bytes&lt;br/&gt;
commons-io display     : 1 GB&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Appears to be more than just a rounddown, because it will knock over 3 gig to 2 gig as well. Odd stuff.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
